<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[mince meat, then add remaining ingredients and process]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[form into 4 meatballs]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[make a paste with cornstarch and soy sauce, a bit water if required, and coat meatballs with it - keep rest]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[deep fry meatballs 2/3 m, then remove]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
fry pak choi in same oil until wilted]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[place in pirex dish, put meatballs on top, pour remaining ingredients, cover in foil]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[steam 40 miuntes, turning meatballs over halfway - alternatively cook normally on stove]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
when cooked, pour stock in heated wok with remaining paste (3), and reudce, 2m ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[season with salt and pepper and pour over meatballs]]></step>
</directions>
